For Loops:          ****for each item in list****

for $var in {list,or comma separated items};
do
  commands
done
___________________________________________________________________________________________

While Loops:        ****while a condition is true****

while [ tests ]
do
  commands
done
___________________________________________________________________________________________

Until Loops:        ****until a condition is true****

until [ tests ]
do
  commands
done
___________________________________________________________________________________________

Break:

breaks out of a loop
___________________________________________________________________________________________

Continue:

continues past... basically a place holder that allows the code to continue without errors
